{"tid":1658614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 長文慎入 有証據指陳同學一定係他殺","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T14:18:37.000Z","uid":80336,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9977c18a998a1c88da8bfbe941ca8312741598","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"開始前同大家講聲對唔住先 呃左大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我想同大家講既係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳同學可能真係有機會係自殺</span></span><br />\n我知我係呢個時間講自殺 係一定會比你地屌我帶風向 五毛 HELLO SIR <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但自殺既動機未必係黑警 刀手 而可能係學校本身 </span></strong></span><br />\n我係一位初初入行做社工既人 對於情緒控制 危機處理(自殺) 唔係一個好有經驗既人<br />\n但希望能夠同大家抱住少少同理心去理解陳同學既內心世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好唔記得大家日日做神探既最終目的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 搵出真相</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYsT1ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYsT1ee.jpg&h=740425fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇返陳同學事情發生既前既野先<br />\n8月12日 東涌站哭成淚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳同學當日曾經係地鐵站情緒激動 係因為佢男友DADDY比人搭左 佢好掛住&amp;擔心男友<br />\n但佢講野既時候內容好模糊 可能因為仍當時情緒唔穩定<br />\n所以我地見到既野只係佢情緒曾經唔穩定過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而重點係係9月19日當日其實陳同學有幾個重覆性行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包括<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">按LIP </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjpZXwk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjpZXwk.png&h=5392b1fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daFVvRn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaFVvRn.png&h=43f094fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3pOQRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3pOQRo.png&h=9e1fba43&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKgEXwq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKgEXwq.png&h=22754a4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搞手繩</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u447m6W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu447m6W.png&h=b18079f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwwd16W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuwwd16W.png&h=b44e3c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋來回行</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkMNm7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkMNm7v.png&h=d4ba1872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFBBfsw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFBBfsw.png&h=df741fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9aa4kR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9aa4kR.png&h=ab12cfc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一種行為係強迫性重覆，係精神上一種障礙，指的是一個人固執地、不斷地重覆某些似乎毫無意義的活動，或反覆重溫某些痛苦的經歷和體驗。 <br />\n而當一個人心理健康唔完全既時候，我地唔會叫佢精神病，但唔代表佢完全好健康，1D事都冇<br />\n而自殺係需要一種極大既衝動，所以若果假定陳同學係自殺，必須要有人刺激到佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關鍵係第一條片係搭LIP上去交野既時候，係咪有教畜對佢講過D咩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到陳同學要搭LIP上7樓周圍望(LWL 天台)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以 無論陳同學係他殺/自殺 都必須有人負上嚴責 政府都係始作俑者</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">最後陳同學希望你能夠安息<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n黑警死全家 No One Is Innocent</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5629982a3b90fa1b0ee0f55cdbf2da2eed780716","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"bb305a23c72a5134acd4b1dd689fdb01a4a28eab","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"241d02c59875f9df6db511f33eb8715fd462f048","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"7051e80bba8ac8046ae568193a14e182c5e699d4","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"252c3d7e77c4d874a0375de11581455497901073","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"e5086260f930908452aafa84465ca3e1bbd96973","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"b5af752a83032888d2e5639f734350bf0d3b0881","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"自推7/10"},{"pid":"8a934ab5ff3693f35f7ade459bf844739d1c8a83","tid":1658614,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"自推8/10"},{"pid":"bd2d293035bb42279a548d86